data.description: Absolutely a GEM in the heart of everything !  Such great curb appeal sitting high above others,  welcoming front porch leads into split level with large family room, huge windows with such great natural lighting.  Dining room and eat in kitchen with breakfast bar.  Primary suite has lots of room and second bedroom up as well.  Downstairs laundry and three more bedrooms makes enough space for in laws quarters, game room, teenager's dream or a large family's needs for sure !  Big fenced in back yard with  feeling of seclusion, two car garage and outdoor storage building.  So much to offer, come see 22 Nob Hill Cove and fall in love !
